Description: |-
    Hermes Agent Fork is an independent community fork. It is not official Nous Research or Teknium software.

    The Android app uses the com.mobilefork.hermesagent application ID to make the fork status explicit and avoid confusion with the original Hermes project.

    It provides local model chat, voice input, resumable model downloads, and Android workflow tools for files, app launch, accessibility-assisted UI actions, notifications, settings helpers, shortcuts, widgets, and automation records.

